বিশ্ববাসীর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_010_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11816,"position":32,"arabic":"١٠","translation":"(১০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":11,"arabic":"وَلَيَعْلَمَنَّ ٱللَّهُ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَلَيَعْلَمَنَّ ٱلْمُنَٰفِقِينَ","translation":"[Yea-] and most certainly will God mark out those who have [truly] attained to faith, and most certainly will He mark out the hypocrites.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3351.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":13115,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَيَعْلَمَنَّ","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই জেনে নিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13116,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌ (বাস্তব ময়দানে)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13117,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13118,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13119,"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَيَعْلَمَنَّ","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই (বাস্তবে) জেনে নিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13120,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","translation":"মুনাফিকদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_011_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13121,"position":7,"arabic":"١١","translation":"(১১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":12,"arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لِلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ ٱتَّبِعُوا۟ سَبِيلَنَا وَلْنَحْمِلْ خَطَٰيَٰكُمْ وَمَا هُم بِحَٰمِلِينَ مِنْ خَطَٰيَٰهُم مِّن شَىْءٍ ۖ إِنَّهُمْ لَكَٰذِبُونَ","translation":"And [He is aware, too, that] they who are bent on denying the truth speak [thus, as it were,] to those who have attained to faith: “Follow our way [of life], and we shall indeed take your sins upon ourselves!” But never could they take upon themselves aught of the sins of those [whom they would thus mislead]: behold, they are liars indeed!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3352.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":14407,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14408,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14409,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14410,"position":4,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের)-কে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14411,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14412,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱتَّبِعُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা অনুসরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14413,"position":7,"arabic":"سَبِيلَنَا","translation":"পথকে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14414,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلْنَحْمِلْ","translation":"আর অবশ্যই আমরা বহন করবো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14415,"position":9,"arabic":"خَطَـٰيَـٰكُمْ","translation":"ত্রুটিগুলোর (পাপরাশিকে)তোমাদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14416,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"কিন্তু না","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14417,"position":11,"arabic":"هُم","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14418,"position":12,"arabic":"بِحَـٰمِلِينَ","translation":"বহনকারী হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14419,"position":13,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14420,"position":14,"arabic":"خَطَـٰيَـٰهُم","translation":"ত্রুটিগুলোর (পাপরাশিকে)তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_012_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14421,"p